== SOURCE

https://deepmind.com/blog/article/alphazero-shedding-new-light-grand-games-chess-shogi-and-go

== AGENT

DeepMind

== GOAL

To create a system that could teach itself to beat any champion in chess, Shogi and go.

== DATA

The only data it needs is the basic rules of the game. The rest of the data is obtained through trial and error by playing games against itself.

== METHODS

Monte Carlo and artificial neural network

== RESULTS

They outperformed any standard AI system and AlphaGO in far less processing power.

== ISSUES

No issues at all

== SCORE

10

== COMMENTS

Good contribution and teaches masters of the game new dynamic unknown strategies.
